tion_bias.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADistinction+bias\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Spring-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Spring_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.spring.org.uk/2008/05/how-to-avoid-choosing-wrong-job-or.php\">\"How To Avoid Choosing the Wrong Job or House: Fight the Distinction Bias\"</a>. Psyblog<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 January</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=How+To+Avoid+Choosing+the+Wrong+Job+or+House%3A+Fight+the+Distinction+Bias&amp;rft.pub=Psyblog&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spring.org.uk%2F2008%2F05%2Fhow-to-avoid-choosing-wrong-job-or.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADistinction+bias\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-International_Journal_of_Selection_and_Assessment-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-International_Journal_of_Selection_and_Assessment_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Brooks, Margaret; Guidroz, Ashley M.; Chakrabarti, Madhura (12 November 2009). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1468-2389.2009.00480.x/abstract\">\"Distinction Bias in Applicant Reactions to Using Diversity Information in Selection\"</a>. <i>International Journal of Selection and Assessment</i>. <b>17</b> (4): 377\u2013390. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2389.2009.00480.x\">10.1111/j.1468-2389.2009.00480.x</a><span class