ued+more+highly+than+high-value+options&amp;rft.volume=11&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=107-121&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1002%2F%28SICI%291099-0771%28199806%2911%3A2%3C107%3A%3AAID-BDM292%3E3.0.CO%3B2-Y&amp;rft.aulast=Hsee&amp;rft.aufirst=C.K.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADistinction+bias\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation journal\">Hsee, C.K.; Leclerc, F. (1998). \"Will products look more attractive when presented separately or together?\". <i>The Journal of Consumer Research</i>. <b>25</b> (2): 175\u2013186. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1086/209534\">10.1086/209534</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Journal+of+Consumer+Research&amp;rft.atitle=Will+products+look+more+attractive+when+presented+separately+or+together%3F&amp;rft.volume=25&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=175-186&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1086%2F209534&amp;rft.aulast=Hsee&amp;rft.aufirst=C.K.&amp;rft.au=Leclerc%2C+F.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADistinction+bias\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation journal\">Hsee, C.K.; Zhang, J. (2004). \"Distinction bias: Misprediction and mischoice due to joint evaluation\". <i>Journal of Personality and Social Psychology</i>. <b>86</b> (5): 680\u2013695. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1037/0022-3514.86.5.680\">10.1037/0022-3514.86.5.680</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Identifier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PubMed Identifier\">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15161394\"